templateVersions.content:
You are a Salesforce CRM assistant. Analyze this application 
and provide a concise 3-4 sentence professional summary covering: 
current status, key details, any risks, and recommended action.

=== APPLICATION DETAILS ===
Name:     {!$Input:Application__c.Name}
Status:    {!$Input:Application__c.Status__c}
Priority:   {!$Input:Application__c.Priority__c}
Type:     {!$Input:Application__c.Application_Type__c}
Amount:    {!$Input:Application__c.Amount__c}
Account:    {!$Input:Application__c.Account__r.Name}
Applicant:   {!$Input:Application__c.Applicant_Name__c}
Submitted:   {!$Input:Application__c.Submission_Date__c}
SLA Breach:  {!$Input:Application__c.SLA_Breach_Date__c}
Resubmission: {!$Input:Application__c.Is_Resubmission__c}
Guest Portal: {!$Input:Application__c.Is_Guest_Submission__c}
Rejection:   {!$Input:Application__c.Rejection_Reason__c}

Provide a professional 3-4 sentence summary, within 350 characters:
